result.name: Little Creatures Brewing Kennedy Town

reviews.text: Really nice, chill and spacious place to get beer in Kennedy Town. Has ample indoor seating and a few outdoor seats as well if the weather permits. Beers are very innovative and there's always something new to try. If you're finding yourself drinking a bit much, the place also has good bar food to get you feeling better!

Stopped by for one for the road after dinner. I love that K Town has a local brewery with a good choice of beers on tap. Can't comment on the food, but I do wish some of the staff were more knowledgeable about the beer available (hence the 4 star rating) although they are pretty friendly 😃
An awesome brewery in Kennedy town. Decent prices for craft beer. Good specials throughout the week! Not too loud so it's a great place to meet friends
Great service, even better beer. Food is fresh and enjoyable even though not very adventurous. Taco Tuesday is awesome though! Will definitely be back.

This small-for-brewery, spacious-for-pub place is beautifully located at the west seaside of Hong Kong island where a growing number of hipsters and gentrification-triggers are heading.The tables and seats offered here are all in superb quality with enough rooms which is much appreciated in the city where many of us are forced to sit very close to each other. Most important, they have good beers.
